metadata.name: Search It
metadata.description:
Search It lets you quickly search the web using search engines like Google, Yandex, Bing, and more, 
directly from the chat, formatting menu, or via command.


Usage:

- Chat menu: tap Plugins ‚Üí Search to open the search box.

- Formatting menu: select a word or text and choose Search to see results.

- Command: type .sr <term> for direct results, or just .sr to open the search box.


You can configure your preferred search engine or a custom URL in settings with .panel.


by @ApplePlugins Lab ‚Ä¢ @exteraDevPlugins

metadata.description:
Shows and controls the current playing track with a styled preview.

Supported services:
‚Ä¢ Spotify (API)
‚Ä¢ Last.fm (scrobble)

How to use:
‚Ä¢ Use .now to show the current playing track (Spotify)

‚Ä¢ Use .stats to show the current playing track (Stats.fm)

‚Ä¢ Use .help to see all available commands
